WEBVTT

00:05.605 --> 00:08.071
♪ Hey, yo ♪

00:08.074 --> 00:10.708
♪ Every day summer
when you MIA ♪

00:10.710 --> 00:13.143
♪ And I can hit the beach
in Californ-I-A ♪

00:13.145 --> 00:15.312
♪ Getting ladies,
getting money ♪

00:15.314 --> 00:16.780
♪ That's my occupation ♪

00:16.782 --> 00:18.215
♪ You know I'm all about ♪

00:18.217 --> 00:20.251
♪ That Californication... ♪
Hey!

00:22.255 --> 00:23.787
Take cover.

00:45.878 --> 00:49.878
<b><font color="#00FF00">♪ NCIS: LA 9x02 ♪</font></b>
<font color="#00FFFF">Se Murio El Payaso</font>
